nodes.text: Ulabos was a frozen, rocky planet in the Coruscant system. It was surrounded by large rings of ice and rock.

In Star by Star, the Yuuzhan Vong invasion fleet crossed Nabatu's orbit before the Ulabos ice ring. This may indicate that Ulabos is closer to Coruscant Prime than Nabatu at some points in its orbit, similar to the orbits of Pluto and Neptune in our solar system.
